name: House Plant #002
description:
The pandemic is forcing us to stay at home. 
a condition which initially is not very easy to get through it. 
seeking to avoid the bustle of the madness.

Growing plants at home is an escape from the world that is not fine. 
It's like entering a world where there's only me and my plants. 
Shady and peaceful. a place to spend time and talk. 
yes. with plants.
